edu.cmu.cs.plural.annot
Annotation Type Imm

@Target(value={METHOD,CONSTRUCTOR,PARAMETER,FIELD})
public @interface Imm

Immutable permissions grant read-only access and guarantee that no modifications to the referenced object will be made.

Author:
Kevin Bierhoff
See Also:
To aggregate this annotation., To annotate a method result., For more complex method specifications.
